:23:22.000Z","msg":"對的時間錯的人一定係之前有遺憾先覺得係錯<br />\n可惜不是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cc82098004fd034a0d58ceccf75be88a1ad626","tid":253751,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我前排同時經歷緊呢兩樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣同時經歷？</blockquote><br />\n同女友中學識<br />\n一直拍到而家7年好深感情<br />\n但有好多解決唔到嘅問題<br />\n漸漸因爲呢個原因失去咗份愛<br />\n同朋友識咗好短時間<br />\n但性格價值觀完全好夾 一見如故<br />\n大家都各自有伴侶<br />\n大家知道大家都鍾意對方<br />\n但選擇只係做一對朋友 得閒update下近況<br />\n已經足夠了"},{"pid":"bc4578b2909e0b146cf57bd9eb3df56eb80ce6a6","tid":253751,"uid":64985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對的時間錯的人可以搵過<br />\n錯的時間對的人你永遠搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20c35e51ce39294b7cc096d122f6efe68e6425e","tid":253751,"uid":68806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"錯的時間對的人sad好多<br />\n利申:試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}